value.query: SELECT %vlocity_namespace%__Status__c, %vlocity_namespace%__OmniScriptSubType__c, %vlocity_namespace%__OmniScriptType__c, %vlocity_namespace%__ObjectId__c, %vlocity_namespace%__ResumeLink__c, %vlocity_namespace%__LastSaved__c FROM %vlocity_namespace%__OmniScriptInstance__c ORDER BY %vlocity_namespace%__LastSaved__c DESC LIMIT 10
